# ====================================================================
# 1. IGNORE HEAVY BINARIES & DATABASES (The "No-Go" Zone)
# ====================================================================
SAVE/
database/
*.tar.zst
*.save/
*.xsf*
*.wfc*
ndb.*
r_*
STORE_REPORT.txt
slurm-*
# ====================================================================
# 2. IGNORE LARGE REPORTS (Keep only the newest or specific ones)
# ====================================================================
# Yambo generates many r_* setup and log files. 
# Usually, you only need the final one.
r-* 
# ====================================================================
# 3. TRACK ESSENTIALS (The "Intelligence" Zone)
# ====================================================================
# We want these even if they are in subfolders
!*.in*
!o-*
!o.*
!info
!*.py
!*.pdf
!*.png
!*.jpeg
!*.sh
